positive.review:
Love this game, happy combination of:
relaxing (when your enemies are stricken and you send out a pair of light cruisers to raid their ports); 
involving (making a 1000 little adjustments and compromises to design the best ship for its role);
challenging (playing as a weaker country and... trying to survive your first 10 years or so...!) and;
great fun (using your little creations to blast huge chunks out of the enemy battleships, dodging torpedoes, launching your monstrous new dreadnought on an unsuspecting foe...!). 

10/10; I usually play with DIP mods.

